summary: Can you write one with Y/N thinking Harry cheated on her but he didn’t? Angst with happy ending please? 😊
question: Can you write one with Y/N thinking Harry cheated on her but he didn’t? Angst with happy ending please? 😊
answer:
A/N: Sure!!! Sorry that took me so long x Enjoy ♡
and thank you @flyingmykite for helping me with this piece!!

Warnings: Angst, fluff, swearing.

Harry hasn’t been home for a week. It’s not like this hasn’t happened before, but it was for work. She usually would call him, and if he’s busy, he would decline her call and reply with a text saying something like: “Hey angel, I’m gonna be busy in the next couple of hours. I’ll be home soon xx” or some kissy emojis. Y/N isn’t really a clingy girlfriend. There are times when she really misses Harry, usually when he isn’t home for months on tour, she’ll send him video messages. 

But this time however, Y/N felt weird. Harry was acting strange and distant. At first, she couldn’t get a hold of his schedule and couldn’t contact him. When she asks him, Harry would just tell her that he’s “working on something.” 

And everytime she shows would her affection towards Harry, he would act cold and distant. Y/N couldn’t help but think “Does he not love me anymore?”

She tried to calm herself down, telling herself Harry’s just really busy. But the other side of her is telling her that maybe Harry is cheating on her with some girls probably much beautiful than her. 

There’s this one time when she walked into him talking on the phone, saying things like “No, Y/N didn’t suspect a thing. She’s in the kitchen.” And before Harry hangs up, she left quietly without him knowing.

“Is he cheating on me?”

Hearing him saying words like these makes her suspicious.She had always thought of marrying Harry. She was almost sure that he’s the one for her.  

was. She’s not sure anymore.

Y/N is heading to the cafe where their first date were, because Harry suddenly suggested that they go on a date. As she’s driving, she thought about what Harry said on the phone that day. 

“Is he going to break up with me?” 

She arrived at the cafe, immediately saw Harry sitting at the place they had their first date on, looking nervous.

“He’s definitely gonna break up with me.”

She sat opposite him, with a worrying look on her face. 

“Y/N.” Her heart instantly dropped into the stomach with his tone. He’s serious. Harry doesn’t usually call your name, he said it’s too ‘distant.’

He calls her name when Y/N has done something wrong or that one time that they argue about him not being home for her during an important events.She thought about so much of the little things they did together. 

“I don’t want a break up, Harry.” Y/N speaks first, trying to hold her tears. “Even if you’re cheating on me.”

“Wait what? Angel, where did you get the idea from?” Harry furrowed his brows, got up from his seat and went to her. He hold her shoulders gently. “Tell me, doll.”

“I…I overheard you on the phone saying that I didn’t suspect anything… and you haven’t been home for a week, you didn’t even tell me you love me.” Y/N said, tears rolling down her cheeks.

“Oh puppy…” He smiled a little, placed a kiss on her forehead and wiped off her tears. “I’m terribly sorry for not replying your calls and messages. I really was busy with something, but I’m not cheating on you.” 

Harry got down on one knee, took out a velvet red box and opened it. “Y/N Y/L/N, Will you do me the honor of becoming my wife?”

“Oh…” Y/N covered her mouth with one hand, looking at him totally shocked.

“Will you?” Harry asked her nervously. 

“Yes…Yes! Definitely a yes.” Y/N jumped into her fiancé arms, sobbing. “I thought…”“I was talking to your mum on the phone, baby.” Harry kissed the top of her head. “Our mom.” 

“I love you, Harry.”

“Love you too, poppet.”

Masterlist

body:
Oh lift me from the grass! I die! I faint! I fail! Let thy love in kisses rain On my lips and eyelids pale. My cheek is cold and white, alas! My heart beats loud and fast;— Oh! press it to thine own again, Where it will break at last.

5. I arise from dreams of thee

“Umm well… you see, we all had no idea what’s going on, most of the time we only skype or chat, we all are just to busy…”“ I completely understand, she was incredibly secretive about her…
